 <span data-ttu-id="565c4-150">有关默认行为时启用了安全修整，请参阅"备注"中<xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider.IsAccessibleToUser%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-150">For the default behavior when security trimming is enabled, see "Remarks" in <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider.IsAccessibleToUser%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="565c4-151">之后<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>对象分析并加载站点地图数据的所有已加载<xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode>对象和<xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection>集合都是只读的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-151">After the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> object parses and loads site map data, all loaded <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode> objects and <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection> collections are made read-only.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="565c4-152">当<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>分析<xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode.Url%2A>属性从站点地图文件，它将转换应用程序相对 Url，以及相对 Url，为应用程序绝对虚拟路径。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-152">When the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> parses the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode.Url%2A> property from a site map file, it converts application-relative URLs, as well as relative URLs, to application-absolute virtual paths.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="565c4-153"><xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> .Sitemap 文件的文件更改通知订阅。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-153">The <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> subscribes to file change notifications for the .sitemap file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="565c4-154">如果对.sitemap 文件进行任何更改<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>重新加载，并重新生成站点地图结构。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-154">If any change is made to the .sitemap file, the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> is reloaded, and the site map structure is rebuilt.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="565c4-155">下面的代码示例演示如何创建的新实例<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>类，并将其初始化以生成从 XML 数据的站点映射。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-155">The following code example demonstrates how to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> class and initialize it to build a site map from XML data.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
<%@ Page Language="c#" %>  
 <!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN">  
 <SCRIPT runat="server">  
 private void Page_Load(object sender, System.EventArgs e)  
 {  
     // Create an instance of the XmlSiteMapProvider class.  
     XmlSiteMapProvider testXmlProvider = new XmlSiteMapProvider();  
     NameValueCollection providerAttributes = new NameValueCollection(1);  
     providerAttributes.Add("siteMapFile","test.sitemap");  
     // Initialize the provider with a provider name and file name.  
     testXmlProvider.Initialize("testProvider", providerAttributes);  
  
     // The BuildSiteMap method is implicitly called when the   
     // RootNode propety is accessed.  
  
     // Prints "/myvirtualdirectory/WebForm1.aspx"  
     Response.Write(testXmlProvider.RootNode.Url + "<BR>");  
     // Prints "/myvirtualdirectory/WebForm2.aspx"  
     Response.Write(testXmlProvider.CurrentNode.Url + "<BR>");  
 }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="565c4-156">前面的代码示例使用 XML 文件中的虚拟根目录的 ASP.NET 应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-156">The preceding code example uses an XML file that is located in the virtual root of the ASP.NET application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="565c4-157">该文件的格式如下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-157">The file has the following format:</span></span>  
  
```  
<siteMap>  
     <siteMapNode title="RootNode" description="The root page." url="WebForm1.aspx">  
         <siteMapNode title="CurrentNode" description="Some sub page." url="WebForm2.aspx"/>  
     </siteMapNode>  
 </siteMap>  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="565c4-245"><xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>类重写继承<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider.Initialize%2A>方法以将应用多个属性，例如`siteMapFile`并`description`属性，为`attributes`集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-245">The <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> class overrides the inherited <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider.Initialize%2A> method to apply several attributes, such as the `siteMapFile` and `description` attributes, to the `attributes` collection.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="565c4-246">下面的代码示例演示如何创建的新实例<xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider>类，并将其初始化以生成从 XML 数据的站点映射。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-246">The following code example demonstrates how to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.XmlSiteMapProvider> class and initialize it to build a site map from XML data.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
<%@ Page Language="c#" %>  
<SCRIPT runat="server">  
 private void Page_Load(object sender, System.EventArgs e) {  
     // Create an instance of the XmlSiteMapProvider class.  
     XmlSiteMapProvider testXmlProvider = new XmlSiteMapProvider();  
     NameValueCollection providerAttributes = new NameValueCollection(1);  
     providerAttributes.Add("siteMapFile","test.sitemap");  
  
     // Initialize the provider with a provider name and file name.  
     testXmlProvider.Initialize("testProvider", providerAttributes);  
  
     // Call the BuildSiteMap to load the site map information into memory.  
     testXmlProvider.BuildSiteMap();  
  
     // Prints "/myvirtualdirectory/WebForm1.aspx"  
     Response.Write(testXmlProvider.RootNode.Url + "<BR>");  
  
     // Prints "/myvirtualdirectory/WebForm2.aspx"  
     Response.Write(testXmlProvider.CurrentNode.Url + "<BR>");  
 }  
 </SCRIPT>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="565c4-247">前面的代码示例使用 XML 文件中的虚拟根目录的 ASP.NET 应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-247">The preceding code example uses an XML file that is located in the virtual root of the ASP.NET application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="565c4-248">该文件的格式如下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="565c4-248">The file has the following format:</span></span>  
  
```  
<siteMap>  
  <siteMapNode title="RootNode" description="The root page." url="WebForm1.aspx">  
    <siteMapNode title="CurrentNode" description="Some sub page." url="WebForm2.aspx"/>  
  </siteMapNode>  
</siteMap>  
```
